Q_NAME: ARRANGING BULIDING BLOCKS FROM SMALLEST TO LARGEST
Q_DESC:
A little girl keshab received a gift from her beloved friend. She found numbers written in a building blocks. she wish to arrange the building blocks in an ascending order. Your task is to write a code to arrange the contents in the given array of building blocks from smallest to largest.
Input:
Input should contain the number of building blocks  n
And input the integers up to the limit n
Output:
It should print the arranged building block elements in the array from smallest to largest.
